        <p class="tdbc-lead tdbc-ink--gray tdbc-mt-md">
        <span class="tdbc-row">
          <span>A series by <a href="https://thinkdobecreate.com/">Stephanie Eckles</a></span> <a href="https://twitter.com/5t3ph/" class="tdbc-icon-button" aria-label="Twitter">
